name: Narmaya (Granblue Fantasy)
description:
Narmaya from Granblue Fantasy, including all her separate official outfits. Trained using animefull-final as the base model at a network dim of 128 and resolution of 640.

The following tags are used for her and the outfits:

Character: narmaya

Default outfit: black dress, white coat

Summer: white bikini

Holiday: santa dress

Valentine: black sweater, apron

The Black Butterfly: black bikini, hood

Grand: red dress

Visions of Butterflies: purple kimono, bandages

Yukata: yukata

The coat can be taken off in her default outfit by leaving the tag out, same goes for the hood in the Black Butterfly costume.
